rows.label: fev08_090_175_msg0003
rows.name:
Much as I would like to find Lady
Meleph without a moment's delay,
it's not wise to overexert ourselves.

rows.label: fev08_090_175_msg0004
rows.name:
Rex in particular is only Driver
we have right now, so would be
dangerous for Rex to tire self out.

rows.label: fev08_090_175_msg0005
rows.name: I wouldn't say I'm worn out just yet...

rows.label: fev08_090_175_msg0006
rows.name:
But you're probably right.
Better to be safe than sorry.

rows.label: fev08_090_175_msg0007
rows.name:
Shin... Do you think this area
seems safe enough?

rows.label: fev08_090_175_msg0008
rows.name: Yes. I don't sense any hostile presence.
